dc_title_s: Maps of the missions of the American Board of Commissioners for Foreign Missions. September, 1851.
dct_alternativeTitle_sm: Maps of the missions of the American Board of Commissioners for Foreign Missions. September\, 1851.
dc_description_s: Maps include: West African Mission, South African Mission, Mission to Syria, Mission to the Armenians, Mission to the Nestorians, Mission to the Mahrattas, Madras and Madura Missions, Madura and Ceylon Missions, Mission to Borneo, Missions to China, Fuh-Chau Mission, Mission to the Sandwich Islands.
